Sabor Boricua!           by JR "Mr. Descarga" Don Perignon & Orquesta Puertorriquena have been around for at least 25 years producing 1st rate material. There is some heavyweight material on this terrific release with the excellent singing of Rico Walker, Junior Gonzalez, and Wicky Gonzalez. The band is blistering with musical artistry and Don Perignon dominates the Timbales with rhythm and elegance. Serious Aficionados of this genre need to own this outstanding production.
